  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This database will be used to better understand the sleep problems of people with SMS. This
      clinical database will be a part of a larger Smith-Magenis Patient Registry used to create an
      awareness campaign around SMS and the sleep disturbances that are characteristic of the
      disorder.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
